elements.name: Launch Appian process and verify Work Type = 'Amend Details' and Work sub-type = 'Letter of Authority'

steps.name: I open appian login page "https://bpm-uat.targetgroup.corp.local/suite/tempo/news/participating"
I enter appian username "VIKASHKUMA" and password "Todayis10%"
I click on the appian login button
I should be navigated to appian home page
I click on the Actions tab
I scroll down and click on Launch Appian Process
I select the portfolio name "Chetwood" and click on Next
I enter the account number "120032" in the Entity Id field and click on Next
I select worktype "Client Correspondence", worksubtype "Returned Cheque" and user group "CSL1"
I enter notes "Test notes for UW" in the Summary Text and Notes field
I click on Launch Process
The Process Launch Confirmation screen should be displayed and closed
I navigate to the TASK tab
I open Single Step Tasks
I click on Show Report Filters
I filter with portfolio "Chetwood", worktype "Client Correspondence" and worksubtype "Returned Cheque"
The launched process should be displayed as a task
I select the respective "Returned Cheque" task and click on it
I click on the Accept Task button
I click on the Complete Task button
I enter notes "Customer Management" in the UW Summary Notes field and click on Submit button
I open UWUat login page "https://uat1-servicing.targetgroup.corp.local/SignOnUAT/login.xhtml"
I enter UWUat username "VIKASHKUMA" and password "Todayis121%Vikash"
I click on the UWUat login button
I validate the UW home screen is displayed
I click on Chetwood BAU and validate the Chetwood home page is displayed
I enter account number "120032" in the Agreement Number field and click on search
I click on Account Detail and validate the popup is displayed
I click on the Verified button and validate the Account Detail home page is displayed
